01:17:31.257 --> 01:17:32.288
Anna!

01:17:32.382 --> 01:17:34.591
Mojbog.
-Me slišiš?

01:17:34.680 --> 01:17:37.051
Ljubica, oči je!
-Mami, kopljem jo ven.

